funding llc snapshot people company overview rd legal funding llc provides financial solutions to the legal industry in the united states its solutions include attorney fee acceleration a program that converts settled cases into immediate cash attorneys line of credit a credit line for various purposes and plaintiff settlement funding program for nonrecourse postsettlement funding the company offers solutions for various types of settlements that include personal injury medical malpractices negligence wage and hour disputes wrongful death infant injuries court appointed fees class actions employment discrimination securities class actions product liability mass torts antitrust and courtappointed fees rd legal f rd legal funding llc provides financial solutions to the legal industry in the united states its solutions include attorney fee acceleration a program that converts settled cases into immediate cash attorneys line of credit a credit line for various purposes and plaintiff settlement funding program for nonrecourse postsettlement funding the company offers solutions for various types of settlements that include personal injury medical malpractices negligence wage and hour disputes wrongful death infant injuries court appointed fees class actions employment discrimination securities class actions product liability mass torts antitrust and courtappointed fees rd legal funding was founded in  and is based in cresskill new jersey detailed description  legion drivecresskill nj united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwlegalfundingcom key executives for rd legal funding llc mr roni dersovitz esq founder and chief executive officer mr leo j zatta cpa chief financial officer mr edwin s baldwin executive vice president of business development mr alan kardon vice president and senior counsel compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region  seiu federal credit union united states  financial credit union united states  lumpsum holdi