t funding can be used for a variety of reasons including reinvesting in their practice advertising for new cases continued financing on existing cases or expanding their office for plaintiffs our funding can be used for a variety of reasons including personal and medical expenses rd legal’s fee acceleration product was designed by the founder of rd legal funding roni dersovitz as a former litigator dersovitz intimately understood the problems plaintiffs’ attorneys and their clients have or can deal with while practicing and intuitively designed the product to their advantage “plaintiffs’ attorneys only survive by a steady cash flow so when their fees are delayed it can become detrimental to them i want to see the attorney cash in” says dersovitz “after a settlement is reached plaintiffs may have to wait an extended period of time before they receive compensation we are able to help them as well” a majority of companies in the lawsuit funding space are focused on commercial litigation or presettlement funding rd legal is an originator of postsettlement funding and remains solely dedicated to it today with decades of experience working with a variety of cases they can operate without the restrictions that newer and less experienced companies can sometimes have “many of the companies in the legal funding space can only provide small dollars to a plaintiff or plaintiffs’ attorney who typically needs more than what they can offer that isn’t a problem at rd legal our starting point is  and it can go over  million” says dersovitz related posts news jul   six payment services purchasing girocard network operations from vöbzvd processing gmbh news jul   london lawyers mackrell turner garrett assist with rimilia’s major international growth funding news jul   relaxed approach to risk of tribunal claims needs to change in light of supreme court ruling says joelson’s employment partner comments are closed current print issue advertisements recent posts pp lending disrupts furth